{"tid":1803501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方聲稱民陣與暴力割蓆，港共繼續分化行動","createTime":"2019-12-30T08:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T09:03:50.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"744bf35fd0deb2cee407ae1c5d4fbc52c1ce76bb","tid":1803501,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:47:00.000Z","msg":"係大家討論緊應唔應該大聲咁講「香港獨立，唯一出路」，對家已經用盡方法搞分化<br />\n出不利和平組的消息，焗和平組解釋，狗再用黎煲同勇武割蓆<br />\n<br />\n----------------------<br />\n<br />\n警方指元旦遊行若有暴力事件或需解散<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉銓表示，留意到在警方向民陣元旦遊行批出不反對通知書後，網上廣泛流傳以民陣名義發出的海報，煽惑化人「毋忘報仇，全城裝修」，與民陣一直宣稱的和平示威不同，民陣已公開否認曾作出有關宣傳，警方歡迎民陣與暴力割蓆，呼籲民陣不要協助掩飾或美化暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n警方港島總區警司曾繁瀚表示，如遊行期間有緊急或暴力事件，主辦單位有責任協助警方疏散，當集會或遊行地點不再安全，警方有可能要解散活動，期望民陣及糾察屆時盡力協助警方，呼籲參加者解散。"},{"pid":"c3074367271d5bad8069b73556dbd595907ec06d","tid":1803501,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:47:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功)<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fcontent%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_23%2FPetition_99604.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=07b44435\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html</a><br />\n2. deadline 30/12 (成功)<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_10%2F_01%2FPetition_99914.nc.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=bb9e92ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html</a></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 暫時最後一個 deadline 1/1 <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要36000人</span><br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=b32bd3b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a>"},{"pid":"463fb10b7735e64b6041ff3b73cd8667e6ac7ad1","tid":1803501,"uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:47:43.000Z","msg":"WTF LOL"},{"pid":"5ce7f3850fc972821b4ce3122b178ce873883052","tid":1803501,"uid":165683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:48:01.000Z","msg":"好低手..."},{"pid":"8c70b42abef0ebb574e63d936902c8c04d6c91e3","tid":1803501,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:48:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b42f89a04a4fa7deab7c6e1ae356b13fc7c38c","tid":1803501,"uid":115212,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"//警方歡迎民陣與暴力割蓆//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好心班狗就發下夢啦，人哋幾時割過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59d8a33bce4ac0caeb4619353400f460555967d","tid":1803501,"uid":810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:51:32.000Z","msg":"打稻草人打到咁撚低手真係笑死人<br />\n香港警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357901fd13d3383965a3770fc2583ff0f46ee5d0","tid":1803501,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:54:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7065deb84978dca7809a7e5c2f2a25ef734cf584","tid":1803501,"uid":253442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:55:20.000Z","msg":"狗：求下你地割啦冇招出喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67361548557c30c0c32faed131afc0bc4400124c"